                    ' Learn from experts
                    br
                    | across the world

          .col-md-6
            = link_to 'https://help.sv.co/admissions-to-sv-co/joining-the-sv-co-program/admission-overview', target: '_blank'
              .program-feature__card
                = image_tag 'home/index/program-build-startup.jpg', class: 'img-fluid'
                .program-feature__card-title
                  h3.program-feature__card-title-text.font-regular
                    ' Build a world class product
                    br
                    | with your friends

          .col-md-6
            = link_to 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TfLMV-XkfGw', target: '_blank'
              .program-feature__card
                = image_tag 'home/index/program-events.jpg', class: 'img-fluid'
                .program-feature__card-title
                  h3.program-feature__card-title-text.font-regular
                    ' Showcase your skills at
                    br
                    | SV.CO events

          .col-md-6
            = link_to 'https://help.sv.co/learning-at-sv-co/how-you-learn-at-sv-co/first-steps-in-building-a-product', target: '_blank'
              .program-feature__card
                = image_tag 'home/index/program-ideas.jpg', class: 'img-fluid'
                .program-feature__card-title
                  h3.program-feature__card-title-text.font-regular
                    ' Scholarships upto Rs. 80,000/- up for grabs

      .col-md-5
        = link_to 'https://help.sv.co/learning-at-sv-co/how-you-learn-at-sv-co/build-your-first-product-while-still-in-college', target: '_blank'
          .program-feature__card
            = image_tag 'home/index/program-learn.jpg', class: 'program-feature__college-img'
            .program-feature__card-title
              h3.program-feature__card-title-text.program-feature__card-title-text--big.font-regular
                span.program-feature__card-title-text--big-highlight.font-semibold
                  ' Learn
                br
                ' wherever you are alongside your
                br
                | college degree

  .container
    .text-center.mt-3
      = link_to 'Learn More', 'https://help.sv.co/', class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg home-apply__button', id: 'home-index__programme-learn-more-link'


section.home-testimonial__container.py-5
  .container
    .home-section__head.mb-4
      h2#testimonial.home-section__head-title.text-center.font-black
        | What happens in the program?
      .home-section__head-subtitle.mx-auto
        p.text-center
          | A unique approach to help you become an industry-ready developer

    .row.home-testimonial__box.mx-auto
      .col-md-4.home-testimonial__image-container.p-0
        = link_to 'https://help.sv.co/learning-at-sv-co/what-we-teach-at-sv-co/svco-program-content', target: '_blank' do
          = image_tag 'home/index/framework-thumbnail.jpg', class: 'img-fluid mx-auto home-testimonial__image', alt: "Program Framework"
      .col-md-8.home-testimonial__text.d-flex.justify-content-center.flex-column
        p
          ' The SV.CO six month program is split into <strong>two major tracks - Product Track and Developer Track.</strong>

        p
          ' <strong>Product Track</strong> is where you build your first internet product, starting from idea selection all
          ' the way to product launch.
        p
          ' <strong>Developer Track</strong> is designed to upgrade you from a classroom coder to an ace developer.
        = link_to 'Find out more about our program here.', 'https://help.sv.co/learning-at-sv-co/what-we-teach-at-sv-co/svco-program-content', class: 'mt-3'

section.six-ways-card__container.py-5
  .container
    .home-section__head.mb-4
      h2#benefits.home-section__head-title.text-center.font-black
        | Alumni Talk!
      .home-section__head-subtitle.mx-auto
        p.text-center
          | Hear them narrate their stories
    .row
      .col-md-4
        a#home-index__six-ways-accelerator-video.six-ways-card__box.my-3 href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#profoundis-story-video"
          .six-ways-card__thumbnail
            = image_tag 'home/index/six-ways-join-accelerator.jpg', class: 'img-fluid six-ways-card__thumbnail-image', alt: 'Join a startup accelerator'
