              h3.six-ways-card__thumbnail-head.font-semibold.mb-0
                | Built a world class internet product, got acquired by an American Company
              p.six-ways-card__thumbnail-subhead
                | Story of Profoundis

      .col-md-4
        a#home-index__six-ways-acquihire-video.six-ways-card__box.my-3 href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#z-pay-story-video"
          .six-ways-card__thumbnail
            = image_tag 'home/index/six-ways-get-acqui-hired.jpg', class: 'img-fluid six-ways-card__thumbnail-image', alt: 'Get acqui-hired'
            .six-ways-card__video-time
              | 1:16 mins
            .six-ways-card__play-button-container.d-flex.flex-column.align-items-center.justify-content-center
            .six-ways-card__thumbnail-content
              h3.six-ways-card__thumbnail-head.font-semibold.mb-0
                | Product they built in college helped them get a job
              p.six-ways-card__thumbnail-subhead
                | Z-pay Acquihired by Tally

      .col-md-4
        a#home-index__six-ways-hired-video.six-ways-card__box.my-3 href="#" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#hiring-story-video"
          .six-ways-card__thumbnail
            = image_tag 'home/index/six-ways-get-hired.jpg', class: 'img-fluid six-ways-card__thumbnail-image', alt: 'Get hired by a startup'
            .six-ways-card__video-time
              | 1:42 mins
            .six-ways-card__play-button-container.d-flex.flex-column.align-items-center.justify-content-center
            .six-ways-card__thumbnail-content
              h3.six-ways-card__thumbnail-head.font-semibold.mb-0
                | Student Developer to Product Manager in a million dollar funded startup
              p.six-ways-card__thumbnail-subhead
                | Hiring at SV.CO

      / .mx-auto.mt-3
      /   = link_to 'Learn More', join_path, class: 'btn btn-primary btn-lg home-apply__button', id: 'home-index__six-ways-learn-more-link'

